OL,5,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FFifteen miles south of York, a
OL,7,     Fprolific car thief crashes and
OL,8,     Frolls a stolen car at over 100mph.
OL,9,     FIn Harrogate, the hunt for a
OL,10,     Fdisqualified driver leads to a
OL,11,     Fhigh-speed pursuit.
OL,12,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,13,     FNear York, a young driver in a
OL,14,     Fstolen car is on a suspected high
OL,15,     Fbehind the wheel. The police must
OL,16,     Fmake a move before the reckless
OL,17,     Fman can join a busy motorway and
OL,18,     Fcause more mayhem.
