OL,6,     FReality series following
OL,7,     Fhigh-speed police intercept units.
OL,8,     FThe interceptors assemble in
OL,9,     Fpursuit of a BMW with no
OL,10,     Finsurance, no tax and a suspected
OL,11,     Fbanned driver behind the wheel.
OL,12,G1700 Shoplifters: Caught Red Handed
OL,13,     FThe fight against the rise of
OL,14,     Fshoplifting. In London's West End
OL,15,     Fundercover officers pursue a known
OL,16,     F"dipper", and in Birmingham a
OL,17,     Fstolen bank card scam becomes
OL,18,     Fthreatening. (Ep1)
OL,19,G1800 Home and Away
