OL,5,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FBarnsley Casualty is facing one of
OL,7,     Fits toughest shifts to date. With
OL,8,     Fno children's beds available
OL,9,     Facross the whole of Yorkshire, and
OL,10,     Fa department filling up with
OL,11,     Fchildren.
OL,12,G2100 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,13,     FA 62-year-old finance broker
OL,14,     Ffights for his life after he
OL,15,     Fsuffers a cardiac arrest while out
OL,16,     Fjogging. A 32-year-old labourer is
OL,17,     Fstabbed in the neck and abdomen
OL,18,     Foutside his home.
